                        ║  [q] exit epic (in epic)   [Esc] clear selection                     ║
                        ║                                                                      ║
                        ║  Actions                                                             ║
                        ║  [n] new task   [E] new epic   [N] notifications                     ║
                        ║  [d] dispatch*  [m] move fwd   [M] move back                         ║
                        ║  [x] archive    [D] quick dsp  [g] session/board                     ║
                        ║  [G] session    (epic: jump to subtask tmux)                         ║
                        ║  [l] →archive   [V] epic done  [a] select all                        ║
                        ║  [Space] select  [f] filter repos  [W] wrap up  (task/epic)          ║
                        ║  [T] detach tmux panel  (Review tasks, supports batch)               ║
                        ║  [S] toggle split mode  (side-by-side with agent)                    ║
                        ║  [P] merge PR  [p] open PR in browser                                ║
                        ║  [J/K] reorder item up/down in column                                ║
